<HEADLINE>
FT  06 DEC 94 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1994
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOEL KIBAZO and JEFFREY BROWN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (17).
GILTS (1) BANKS (1) Banco Bilbao Vizcaya, BUILDING &amp; CNSTRN (1) Andrews
Sykes, DISTRIBUTORS (2) Faber Prest, Trifast, DIVERSIFIED INDLS (2) Hawtin,
Whitecroft, ELECTRNC &amp; ELECT EQUP (1) Acal, ENGINEERING (1) Lincat, ENG,
VEHICLES (1) Honda Motor, HOUSEHOLD GOODS (1) Denby, INVESTMENT TRUSTS (3)
Brazilian Inv., Fleming Int'l. High Zero Prf., TR Technology Zero Prf .,
INVESTMENT COMPANIES (1) Mauritius Fund, LEISURE &amp; HOTELS (1) SUPPORT SERVS
(1) MMT Computing.
NEW LOWS (105).
GILTS (8) BREWERIES (2) Fuller STA, Young Brew N/V, BUILDING &amp; CNSTRN (5)
Berkeley, Eve, Lovell (YJ), McAlpine (A), Wilson (C), BLDG MATLS &amp; MCHTS (5)
Cape, Caradon 7 1/4 p Prf., Darby Grp., Heywood Williams Cnv. Prf.,
